      "agentResultText": "All done. Here's what was added:\n\n### Changes\n\n1. **`prisma/schema.prisma`** — Added `Organization` model with `name`, timestamps, and relations to `User` and `Post`. Added `orgId` foreign key to both `User` and `Post`.\n\n2. **`prisma/migrations/20260309010000_add_organizations`** — Migration that creates the `Organization` table, adds `orgId` columns, backfills existing data with a default team, then makes the columns required.\n\n3. **`src/lib/current-user.ts`** — On first sign-in, auto-creates an organization (\"{name}'s Team\") for the user. Returns the user with their `org` included.\n\n4. **`src/app/dashboard/page.tsx`** — Posts are now filtered by `orgId` instead of `authorId`, so all team members see each other's posts. Added an \"Author\" column to the table. Subtitle shows the org name.\n\n5. **`src/app/dashboard/actions.ts`** — `createPost` attaches the user's `orgId`. `updatePost`/`deletePost` scope by `orgId` so users can only modify posts within their org.\n\n6. **`src/app/settings/page.tsx`** — Added an \"Organization\" card showing the team name (editable) and a member list.\n\n7. **`src/app/settings/actions.ts`** — Added `updateOrganization` action to rename the team.",
